name: Perpetual Calendar
description: Taking the theme of Old Wives' Tales, The Nora Whynot Press has produced a beautifully illustrated perpetual calendar. This calendar is an everlasting gift that will permanently preserve all your precious dates - birthdays, anniversaries and other special occasions that will be a reminder year after year. All 12 months including cover are hand printed on recycled boxboard using hand-mixed inks to produce an individual and unique printed calendar. No two are exactly the same. Calendar Specifications Size: 5.11 inch x 13.26 inch (337 x 130mm) Materials: Australian made 100% recycled boxboard, inks, screenprint. Spiral bound with top mounting loop.

name: Vintage Magnets
description: Have some fun on your fridge with Nora's funky vintage range of 'Stick it' magnets. Each pack comes complete with four colourful magnets. These can easily stick to your fridge or magnetic board and are Ideal for attaching photos, notes or other little reminders! A fun and useful gift to keep you or a friend organised. Magnet Specifications Size: Each magnet is 37mm Diameter

name: Garden Cards with Gift Tags
description: Nora says... "You'll dig our new gardening cards!" Each individual hand printed card is blank inside for you to write your own special message and comes complete with a matching gift tag. Nora's garden range is ideal for birthdays, special occasions or just to say hello to a garden lover. Card Details 2 Colour Pass on recycled boxboard, Blank inside, x 1 Green C6 Envelope. Packaged in cello bag with Nora Whynot seal for protection. Size: 6 x 4 inch (148 x 105mm) when folded Materials: Australian made 100% recycled boxboard, twine, inks, screenprint

name: Nora's 'Pets' Folder
description: Nora's Pet folder is part of the 'Nora says... File it!' range of handmade, stylish and practical organisers. It's a great and simple way of keeping your furry friend happy by having all of their important information in one safe place. Nora says... "it's a purrr-fect gift for any pet owner." Folder Specifications Size: 13 inch x 10 1/4 inch (330 x 260mm) Materials: Australian made 100% recycled boxboard, inks, fabric tag, elastic, Buckram bookcloth, screenprint.

name: Brisbane Bus Routes - Collection 1
description: Nora says "Stop that bus!" Collection 1 Based on Brisbane bus routes, Nora has created a stylish collection of 4 different routes from Australia's most livable city - Brisbane. Card Details 2 Colour Pass on recycled boxboard, Blank inside, x 4 White C6 Envelopes. Packaged in cello bag with Nora Whynot seal for protection. Size: 6 x 4 inch (148 x 105mm) when folded Materials: Australian made 100% recycled boxboard, inks, screenprint
